%
% short description what the module does
%
Read module for Sandia Stl data.
 
% input of a module icon for example
% #1  path for eps
% #2  picture name
% #3  scale factor
\begin{covimg2}	{}{ReadStlModule}{0.7}\end{covimg2}

ReadStl converts the representation of a surface in Sandia Stl format
(specified as file browser parameter) to a format acceptable for Covise (on the
first output port, e.g. used as input for the Renderer); in addition, it supplies
normals on the second output port. 

Please note:
ReadStl can read \begin{bf} ASCI files and binary files \end{bf}.
In most cases (less than 1 Million cells), ReadStl will detect the filetype automatically (parameter Format =
autodetect), if not, use manual selection.
%
% short information about versions 
%
The module supports binary input since Release 5.2.3

